Package com.sun.star.comp.helper

Class Summary
Bootstrap Bootstrap offers functionality to obtain a context or simply a service manager.
ComponentContext Component context implementation.
ComponentContextEntry Component context entry for constructing ComponentContext objects.
RegistryServiceFactory Deprecated. use class Bootstrap instead
SharedLibraryLoader Deprecated. use class Bootstrap bootstrapping a native UNO installation and use the shared library loader service.
UnoInfo UnoInfo offers functionality to obtain the UNO jar files.
 

Exception Summary
BootstrapException BootstrapException is a checked exception that wraps an exception thrown by the original target.
